<item>
 <title>Родной край</title>
 <link>https://vse.la/%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B8%D1%85/%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B4%D0%BD%D0%BE%D0%B9-%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B9</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B8%D1%85/%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B4%D0%BD%D0%BE%D0%B9-%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B9&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://vse.la/images/styles/thumb180/public/stihi_images/4a2odkdgtiq.jpg&quot; width=&quot;180&quot; height=&quot;112&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;И всем армянам я того желаю,&lt;br /&gt;
Вернуться к самому родному краю.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-tematika field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Тематика:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tematika/lirika&quot;&gt;Лирика&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tematika/lirika/grazhdanskaya&quot;&gt;Гражданская&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
