<item>
 <title>Я стал хозяйкой на неделю</title>
 <link>https://vse.la/%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B8%D1%85/%D1%8F-%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B0%D0%BB-%D1%85%D0%BE%D0%B7%D1%8F%D0%B9%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%B9-%D0%BD%D0%B0-%D0%BD%D0%B5%D0%B4%D0%B5%D0%BB%D1%8E</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B8%D1%85/%D1%8F-%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B0%D0%BB-%D1%85%D0%BE%D0%B7%D1%8F%D0%B9%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%B9-%D0%BD%D0%B0-%D0%BD%D0%B5%D0%B4%D0%B5%D0%BB%D1%8E&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://vse.la/images/styles/thumb180/public/stihi_images/1-13.jpg&quot; width=&quot;162&quot; height=&quot;140&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Я стал хозяйкой на неделю,&lt;br /&gt;
И мне совсем здесь не уютно.&lt;br /&gt;
Посуду мыть, сгибая шею,&lt;br /&gt;
Я представляю, как им трудно.&lt;/p&gt;
